<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>REPORT_TITLE</title>
    <style media="all" type="text/css">
    html,body{font-family:"Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:.8em;color:#000;background:#fff;margin:0;padding:0;height:100%;overflow:hidden}
    .flex-row-container{display:flex;flex-direction:row;justify-content:space-between;align-items:stretch;align-content:center}
    .fix-top{position:fixed;top:0;right:0;left:0;z-index:9999}
    .hidden-content{display:none;color:#000;text-align:center}
    .tsc-header{height:60px;background-color:#333;padding:0 15px}
    .tsc-header .title{color:#fff;margin:15px;font-weight:400;align-self:center}
    #ts-selection{margin:15px 15px 15px 0;padding:5px;border:1px solid #fafafa;align-self:center}
    .tsc-header a{cursor:pointer;align-self:center}
    .tsc-header img{vertical-align:middle;width:24px;height:24px}
    #ts-container{border:0;margin:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;left:0;right:0;bottom:0}
    </style>
    <style media="print" type="text/css">
    .no-print,.no-print *{display:none!important}
    .hidden-content{display:block}
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header name="tsc-header" class="tsc-header fix-top flex-row-container no-print">
        <div class="flex-row-container">
            <a class="view" href="index.html" title="List View"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8;base64," /></a>
            <h1 class="title">REPORT_TITLE</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="ts-navigation">
            <select id="ts-selection" name="ts-selection"></select>
            <a id="ts-open" href="#" target="_blank" title="Open report in new window"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," width="24" height="24"></a>
        </div>
    </header>
    <h1 class="hidden-content">REPORT_TITLE</h1>
    <p class="hidden-content">This report view does not support printing. Please use List View report.</p>
    <iframe id="ts-container" class="no-print" src="#"></iframe>
    <script type="text/javascript">
    var tsList = JSON.parse('TEST_SUITE_REPORT_LIST');

    function ready(fn) {
        if (document.readyState != 'loading') {
            fn();
        } else {
            document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', fn);
        }
    }

    ready(function() {
        var tsContainer = document.getElementById('ts-container');
        var tsSelection = document.getElementById('ts-selection');
        var tsOpen = document.getElementById('ts-open');

        tsList.forEach(function(item, index) {
            var option = document.createElement('option');
            option.value = item.report;
            option.innerHTML = item.report_location;
            tsSelection.appendChild(option);
            if (index === 0) {
                tsContainer.setAttribute("src", option.value);
                tsOpen.setAttribute("href", option.value);
            }
        });
        tsSelection.selectedIndex = 0;

        tsSelection.addEventListener('change', function(event) {
            var tsUrl = event.target.value;
            tsContainer.setAttribute("src", tsUrl);
            tsOpen.setAttribute("href", tsUrl);
        });
    });
    </script>
</body>

</html>
